item.title: The Power of R and Python
item.description: Using the skills I learned in my computational biology course at UT Austin, I will show a simple, yet effective, way to combine the power of R and Python. NYC is one of my favorite cities to visit. I admire how diverse the city is, as well as the hustle and bustle of people moving in and out every second! For this reason, I have decided to use a dataset that holds flight data from the three NYC area airports from 2013.
